{"tid":2030400,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 施蒙尼死左","createTime":"2020-05-22T17:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T08:55:49.000Z","uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a00adae940f878fc5dc17b1b05aa3610d976ed25","tid":2030400,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:11:07.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】曾帶領國際米蘭贏得歐洲足協盃的名帥施蒙尼於周五離世，終年81歲。<br />\n<br />\n周五對國際米蘭陣營人士而言想必心情復雜，一方面球隊慶祝10年前今日揚威歐聯，成為3冠王，然而又傳來前教練施蒙尼（Luigi Simoni）離世的消息。會方發表聲明指：「今天，5月22日，他（施蒙尼）離開我們。」至於意大利足總會長加雲拿亦公開哀悼：「一名偉大的足球人離我們而去。」施蒙尼於去年曾中風，之後健康狀況一直欠佳。<br />\n<br />\n球員時代司職中場的施蒙尼，於1974年在熱拿亞展開執教生涯，到1997年執掌國際米蘭兵符，到1997/98年的歐洲足協盃（歐霸盃前身）打敗拉素贏得冠軍。當時其麾下猛將包括朗拿度、辛尼迪及森莫蘭奴等。那場決賽，剛好由上述3名球員入波。<br />\n<br />\n「施蒙尼與朗拿度的組合，將會永存所有人，而不僅是國際米蘭球迷的心中。」國際米蘭聲明續道。<br />\n<br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca10db050d4c51ce0d6e4077510b1db208c01f03","tid":2030400,"uid":116330,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"以為馬體會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de7684542d224ac0a6cc78467a4be3d55423f39","tid":2030400,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba682e0c51d24eba999c728804d0317e4795364","tid":2030400,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ca10db050d4c51ce0d6e4077510b1db208c01f03","tid":2030400,"uid":116330,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"以為馬體會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"re